Class DataController

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.team4.controller.DataController
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AirlineTabController, AirportTabController, EmissionsTabController, FlightPathTabController, RouteTabController
    public abstract class DataController
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes the required functionality of all the controllers that display tables of data in their scene.
